{"tid":1771982,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"慎之，慎之 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-12-06T08:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T08:56:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fef5ea7ef5608caa99c85d511753de0ddaa4c574","tid":1771982,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T08:56:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191206/20819703/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F20819703%2F&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=65cfa102\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F20819703%2F&h=6c2e5283\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191206/20819703/</a><br />\n<br />\n慎之，慎之 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191206/large/1575536197_4864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191206%2Flarge%2F1575536197_4864.jpg&h=4bc727e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一月二十四日區議會選舉，中共出盡種票、買票、配票、造票等手段，在朝派還是兵敗如山倒，八成半議席落在民主派手上，港人額手相慶之餘，更應記取歷史教訓。<br />\n<br />\n二零一四年民主佔領運動瓦解之後，所謂本土派崛起，由黃毓民、陳雲領軍，李怡附和，一時聲勢大盛。他們以「先安內，後攘外」為藉口，致力攻擊民主派；又以「打倒共產黨」的空話，炫人目耳。於是二零一五、一六年區議會及立法會選舉，民主派不但未能賈民主佔領運動的餘勇，多奪議席，還因被左右夾攻，議席再削。民主黨何俊仁就是被熱血公民鄭松泰抄擊，保不住屯門樂翠區議席，席位終於讓與中共愛將何君堯。<br />\n<br />\n當年，文壇上我幾乎是唯一力闢黃、陳本土論的不識時務獃子。二人二零一六年參選立法會失利，這獃子或稍有微功。二零一五年十二月二十二日拙欄說：「我不贊同本土派理論，對民主派中人也不盡欣賞。但是，只要他們都不附共，不是一味『分彼此而共鬥』，為國家抗共可也，為香港抗共可也，都值得支持。」這立場我至今不改：今日中國名存實亡，爭什麼「統一」、「獨立」根本沒有意思。大敵當前，港人還不同心協力，外禦其侮，是自取其殃。<br />\n<br />\n是次區議會選舉，港人終於發揮了「不分裂、不割席」的大精神，小勝一仗。但黃、陳即使不捲土重來，也未必繼後無人，慎之，慎之。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"797649c87ebba22dd445cceea5381c272caa7da5","tid":1771982,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"【第十陸期牆紙】回首、向前<br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=aff8b0dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768510/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AVwsVSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAVwsVSd.jpg&h=bc013387&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}